---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro'
---

<MainLayout title="帮助中心">
<header class="bg-surface sticky top-0 z-40 border-b border-outline-variant/60 flex justify-between items-center px-6 h-16 w-full">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4">
<button class="p-2 hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors rounded-full"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface">arrow_back</span></button>
<h1 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-primary">帮助中心</h1>
</div>
<button class="p-2 hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors rounded-full"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface">notifications</span></button>
</header>
<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 pb-24">
<section class="mb-12 text-center">
<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-headline mb-4 tracking-tight">我们能为您提供什么帮助？</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body mb-8">在这里搜索常见问题或浏览下方类别</p>
<div class="relative max-w-2xl mx-auto">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-outline">search</span>
<input class="w-full pl-12 pr-4 py-4 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:border-transparent transition-all outline-none text-on-surface placeholder:text-outline shadow-card" placeholder="搜索关键词，如"定制"、"退货政策"..." type="text"/>
</div>
</section>
<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/40 hover:shadow-card transition-all cursor-pointer group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">package_2</span></div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-semibold mb-2">订单问题</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">追踪物流、修改地址或取消订单的相关指南。</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/40 hover:shadow-card transition-all cursor-pointer group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-tertiary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-tertiary/20 transition-colors"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary">palette</span></div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-semibold mb-2">定制指南</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">了解如何选择材质、颜色及个性化刻字服务。</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-low p-8 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant/40 hover:shadow-card transition-all cursor-pointer group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-secondary/20 transition-colors"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">local_shipping</span></div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-headline font-semibold mb-2">配送与退换</h3>
<p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant font-body">关于全球配送时效、费用及无忧退货流程。</p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="mb-12">
<h2 class="text-2xl font-headline mb-6 border-b border-outline-variant pb-2">热门问题</h2>
<div class="space-y-4">
<details class="group bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-5 cursor-pointer list-none"><span class="font-body font-medium">我的订单什么时候发货？</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">expand_more</span></summary><div class="px-5 pb-5 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">标准订单通常在3-5个工作日内发货。定制产品由于需要手工制作，预计在7-10个工作日内完成并寄出。发货后您将收到包含物流追踪号的确认邮件。</div></details>
<details class="group bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-5 cursor-pointer list-none"><span class="font-body font-medium">如何申请退货？</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">expand_more</span></summary><div class="px-5 pb-5 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">您可以在签收后15天内申请退货。请通过"我的订单"页面选择对应商品，并点击"申请售后"。非质量问题的退货，邮费需由客户承担。</div></details>
<details class="group bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden"><summary class="flex justify-between items-center p-5 cursor-pointer list-none"><span class="font-body font-medium">支持哪些支付方式？</span><span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180">expand_more</span></summary><div class="px-5 pb-5 text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">我们目前支持微信支付、支付宝、银联支付以及各大主流信用卡的在线支付，确保您的交易安全便捷。</div></details>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-primary text-on-primary rounded-2xl p-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8 overflow-hidden relative">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-container opacity-20 rounded-full -mr-20 -mt-20"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 text-center md:text-left"><h2 class="text-3xl font-headline mb-2">仍需进一步帮助？</h2><p class="text-on-primary/80 font-body max-w-md">我们的客服专家全天候在线，随时为您解答疑问并提供个性化建议。</p></div>
<button class="relative z-10 px-8 py-4 bg-surface text-primary font-bold rounded-lg hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all active:scale-95 shadow-lg flex items-center gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">support_agent</span>联系在线客服</button>
</section>
</main>
</MainLayout>
